oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The bottom of the photograph reads, "RCA Victor Records, Hank Snow, The Singing Ranger, Grand Ole Opry and WSM - TV." Snow was born in Canada on May 9, l9l4, and died on Dec. 20, 1999. He was elected into the Country Music Hall of Fame in 1979.
